div.p:
Sebastian, so many;
Corambus, so many; Jaques,
so many;

a Frenchman; what his
reputation is with the
duke;

Nay look not so upon me;
we shall hear of your
lordship anon.

The duke knows him for no
other but a poor officer
of mine;

I moved his majesty to
speak in the behalf of my
daughter;

You beg a single penny
more: come, you shall
ha't;

and by what rough
enforcement you got it
from her:

and things which would
derive me ill will to
speak of;
